    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>[+] Anno ab incarnacione domini nostri Hiesu Cristi millesimo centesimo
                        octavo, indicione prima. Presencia <rs key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines">bonorum
                            ominum</rs> corum [n]omina hic subter leguntur, hi sunt, <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #siblingOf"><name ref="Hodo/de Cerexole"
                                >Odo</name></persName> de <placeName>Cerexole</placeName> et
                            <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #siblingOf"><name
                                ref="Iohannes/de Cerexole">Hio[anne]s</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius et <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Wido/de Vialengo"
                            >Vuido</name></persName> de <placeName>Vialengo</placeName> et <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Wilielmus"
                            >Vuilielmus</name></persName> et <persName key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"
                                ><name ref="Raginmundus">Ragimondus</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines #parentOf"><name ref="Vualdengus"
                                >Vualdengus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#parentOf">pater</rs> eius et <persName
                            key="#Boni_viri/boni_homines"><name ref="Otto/de Reginzo"
                            >Otto</name></persName> de <placeName>Reginzo</placeName>. Ibique in eorum
                        presencia <persName key="#childOf #Decima #Landed_possessions"><name
                                ref="Gandulfus">Gandulfus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#childOf">filius</rs>
                        <persName key="#parentOf"><name ref="Adam/de Calino">Adami</name></persName>
                        de <placeName ref="#places/4158">Calino</placeName> fecit finem et
                        transaccionem et refutacionemc <rs key="#Churches">heclesie</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Cells/hermitages" ref="#juridical_persons/2066"
                            >Sancti Viti</orgName>, silicet <rs key="#Cells/hermitages">celam</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Cells/hermitages" ref="#juridical_persons/2001"
                            >Sancti Benedicti</orgName>, per lingnum quod in suhis tenebat
                        m[anibus], de <rs key="#Decima">decimis</rs> et <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions">bragidis</rs> que fuerunt quondam <persName
                            key="#Count" ref="#people/2181">Uberti</persName>
                        <rs key="#Count">comitis</rs>, de <rs key="#Landed_possessions">pecia una de
                            terra</rs> que est laborata per <persName><name ref="Obizo/de Fontana"
                                >Obizellum</name></persName> de <placeName>Fontana</placeName>; ab
                        uno capite [...] <persName><name ref="Faverisa">Faverisa</name></persName>,
                        ab alio latere filii <persName><name ref="Danihel"
                            >Danielis</name></persName>, ab alio Sanctus Benedicti, alio <rs
                            key="#Roads">via</rs>. Penam insuper se obbligavit conponere <rs
                            key="#Penalty">centum solidorum</rs> super se aut per suos heredes aut
                        per suos missos vel aliquam interpositam personam agere aut causare voluiset
                        de supradictis rebus adversus heclesiam Sancti Vuiti vel adversus aliquos
                        tenentes eam. (S.) Ego <persName key="#Notary #Transactional_breve #Writer"
                            ref="#people/3763">Teuzo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">[no]tarius</rs> rogatus hoc <rs key="#Transactional_breve"
                            >brevem</rs> scribere <rs key="#Writer">scripsi</rs>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
